{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"black","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"Where does magic come from?","narrationEffect":"in","narrationHAlignment":"left","narrationPosX":180.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"If it comes from my emotions,@then where do my emotions come from?"},{"narration":"From tomorrow onward,@my magic will surely come from the past."},{"autoTurnLast":0.8,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"——To all of us who will lose you.——","narrationEffect":"in"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"bg_adv_46114.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":104300,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"id":6114,"name":"sprite_0","pos":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeInTime":1.5,"turnEffect":"ef_adv_10"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime16","chara":[{"id":104300,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Kuroe","textRight":"[surround:1043A01][name:sprite_0:effect_7000_attack01]...Hmph!","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.8,"bgEffect":"shakeSmall","chara":[{"effect":"7002_damage01","id":6114,"name":"sprite_0"}],"surround":"1043A02","textClear":1},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"motion":400}],"nameRight":"Kuroe","textRight":"[surround:1043A07][name:sprite_0:effect_7001_attack02]This...is the end!"},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"bgEffect":"shakeLarge","chara":[{"effect":"7003_damage02","id":6114,"name":"sprite_0"}],"surround":"1043A08","textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":6114,"name":"sprite_0"}],"se":"3102_enemy_dead"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20312.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":104300,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"item":[{"iPhoneXScale":1.0,"path":"resource/scenario/img/51030_fishing_homura/51030_window.png","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"bgFront"}],"se":"7209_gate_close","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"...[wait:1.0][chara:104300:cheek_0][chara:104300:face_mtn_ex_000.exp3.json][chara:104300:eyeClose_1:lipSynch_1]Phew.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":104300,"pos":0}],"textClear":1},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime04","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":800402,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Th-thanks a bunch."},{"chara":[{"id":800402}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"It's impressive that you managed to beat such@a terrifying Witch..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":800402}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"You sure are strong."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":104300,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Not really... I'm just average."},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Anyway, this train is dangerous. Shouldn't you@hurry up and get off?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":800402}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"...I can't yet."},{"chara":[{"id":800402}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Not until I find my father..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":104300,"lipSynch":1,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Is he on the train, too?"},{"chara":[{"id":800402}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"I'm still not sure..."},{"chara":[{"id":800402}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Is he here, or is he waiting at the end of the@tracks...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":800402}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Wherever he is, if I stay on this train..."},{"chara":[{"id":800402}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"...I'm sure I'll find him."},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"...I don't think your father..."},{"chara":[{"id":104300}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"...would want you to put yourself at risk like this,@would he?"},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"If you die, then what's the point?"},{"chara":[{"id":104300}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"You're going to have to get off and..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":800402}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"I'm sorry, I just can't."},{"chara":[{"id":800402},{"id":104300,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"If I get off..."},{"chara":[{"id":800402}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"...I'll never be able to come back here again..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104300,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"That's not true."},{"chara":[{"id":104300}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"As long as you're alive, you can always..."},{"chara":[{"id":800402}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Once we deboard..."},{"chara":[{"id":800402}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"...I'm sure that you and I will both realize..."},{"chara":[{"id":800402},{"id":104300,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"...that this journey won't last forever..."},{"chara":[{"id":800402}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"And yet I still haven't gotten to tell my beloved@father \"thank you\" or \"goodbye\"..."},{"chara":[{"id":800402}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"...even though he's the most important person@in my life."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":104300,"lipSynch":1}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Then, can I help you look for him?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":800402}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Would you really?"},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Yeah... I know how you feel."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104300}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"I have someone incredibly important to me, too..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104300}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"She gave me so many things when I was empty..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Kuroe","narration":"I still haven't gotten to tell her...","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"...\"thank you\" or \"goodbye\", either..."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeInTime":1.5,"turnEffect":"stop"},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bgm":"bgm05_event05"},{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":1,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/adv_eve_1215.ExportJson","zOrder":"charaFront"}],"autoTurnLast":0.1,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bgm":"stop","deleteArmatureList":[1],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
